<item>
            <title>[LU-8129] sanity test_102n: before and after xattrs of &apos;/mnt/lustre/f102n.sanity.1&apos; differ </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8129</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for John Hammond &amp;lt;john.hammond@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/20ada272-179b-11e6-9e5d-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/20ada272-179b-11e6-9e5d-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_102n failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;before and after xattrs of &apos;/mnt/lustre/f102n.sanity.1&apos; differ
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please provide additional information about the failure here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 102n&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The tag 2.8.53 has disabled some conditional code that causes this test to fail. The fix is in &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/20112/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/20112/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
